    "title": "POMPE-C Tool for Pulmonary Embolism Mortality",
    "desc": "The POMPE-C tool predicts mortality for patients with pulmonary embolism with cancer.",
    "data": {
        "orgreference": [
            {
                "href": "https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22475313",
                "text": "Kline JA, Roy PM, Than MP, Hernandez J, Courtney DM, Jones AE, Penaloza A, Pollack CV Jr. Derivation and validation of a multivariate model to predict mortality from pulmonary embolism with cancer: The POMPE-C tool. Thromb Res. 2012 May;129(5):e194-9. doi: 10.1016/j.thromres.2012.03.015. Epub 2012 Apr 3."
