        "evidence": "<p><b>Probability (P) of death using the POMPE-C formula:</b></p>\n<p>P = 100*(1 - 1 / (1 + Exp(3.718 + 1.551*DNR + 0.799*RespDistress + 0.734*Leg Swelling + 1.473*AMS + 1.027*HR + 0.044*RR + (-0.0636*SAT) + (-0.012*Body Weight))))</p>",
