        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\nvar r, u, x, y, z;\nvar wt = parseFloat(wt);\n\nvar dnr = parseFloat(dnr);\nvar resp_dist = parseFloat(resp_dist);\nvar uls = parseFloat(uls);\nvar ams = parseFloat(ams);\nvar hr = parseFloat(hr);\nvar rr = parseFloat(rr);\nvar sat = parseFloat(sat);\nvar wt = parseFloat(wt) * 2.2; // weight comes to us in kilos but for this study actually uses lbs\n\nvar r = 3.718 + (1.551711 * dnr) + (0.799617 * resp_dist) + (0.734339 * uls) +\n  (1.473451 * ams) + (hr * 1.027895) + (0.04422 * rr) + (-0.063644 * sat) + (-\n    0.011613 * wt);\n\nvar u = 1 + (Math.exp(r));\nvar x = 1 / u;\nvar y = 100 * (1 - x);\nvar z = Math.round(y);\n\ncalc_output.push({\n  name: 'mini',\n  value: z,\n  value_text: '%',\n  message: 'Chance of 30-day mortality'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n  name: '2022_POMPE-C Tool_result',\n  value: z,\n  value_text: '%',\n  message: 'Chance of mortality within 30 days.'\n});\n",
